{"to":["academicalliance@university.edu"],"subject":"Upcoming Study Session – Agenda and Prep","body":"Hi Academic Alliance team,

Hope you’re all doing well!

Our next collaborative study session is scheduled for early next week in our usual study space on campus. To help everyone prepare, here’s the high-level agenda we’ll follow:

• Brief review of last week’s key concepts  
• Discussion of new material from Chapters 4 & 5  
• Group exercises focusing on statistical methods  
• Preparation activities for the upcoming mid-term  

Please bring your notes, questions, and any resources you’d like to share. If there’s an additional topic you’d like to slot in, just let me know and I’ll build it into the flow.

Looking forward to another productive session with you all!

Thanks,
Jane"}
